    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Coat</strong> with the pepper, honey, Dijon mustard, garlic, zest and juice of the lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span> with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">(2 tbsp)</span> olive oil and a pinch of salt</p>\r\n<p><strong>Scrunch</strong> up the foil over the chicken, leaving the parcel open</p>\r\n<p><strong>Place</strong> the tray in the oven for an initial 10-15 min</p>",
