    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Drain</strong> and steam-dry the parboiled potatoes</p>\r\n<p><strong>Heat</strong> a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">(2 tbsp)</span> butter over a medium-high heat</p>\r\n<p><strong>Once</strong> the butter has melted, add the potatoes with the rosemary and a big pinch of salt and cook for 3-5 min or until just starting to crisp</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
