      "instruction": "<p><strong>Remove</strong> the tray from the oven, add the potatoes and return the tray to the oven until the chicken has cooked through (approx. 5 min)</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\"><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, return the pan to a medium heat with a knob of butter, then add the kale with a splash of water and a lid</span></p>\r\n<p><strong>Cook</strong> for 4 min or until tender with a slight bite</p>",
